      • flattening

        public double flattening()

      • eccentricity

        public double eccentricity()
        Gets the eccentricity of the ellipse, between 0 (inclusive) and 1 (exclusive)
        Returns:
        e = sqrt(1-(b^2/a^2)), where a=semi-major axis and b=semi-minor axis
